		<title>Correction: The Roundtable — &#8216;Secret Identities: Exploring Student Identity and Social Justice through Comic Books in Higher Education&#8217;</title>
		<link>https://today.uic.edu/corrrection-the-roundtable-secret-identities-exploring-student-identity-and-social-justice-through-comic-books-in-higher-education/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[UIC News staff]]></dc:creator>
